'''尼格罗尼'''（{{lang-it|Negroni}}）是一种流行的[[意大利|意大利]][[鸡尾酒|鸡尾酒]]，由一份[[金酒|金酒]]、一份甜红[[味美思|味美思]]和一份[[金巴利|金巴利]]组成，使用的点缀物是[[橙|橙]]皮。<ref>{{citation |url=https://www.nytimes.com/recipes/1016357/negroni.html |title=Negroni |work=The New York Times |date=2014-05-21 |last=Schaap |first=Rosie |accessdate=2020-08-03 |archive-date=2014-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140527224808/http://www.nytimes.com/recipes/1016357/negroni.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>它被认为是一种[[开胃酒|开胃酒]]。

制作尼格罗尼的传统方法是在加冰块的岩石杯中搅拌（stirred），而不是摇晃（shaken），最后再点缀一片橙子。在意大利以外的地方经常会使用橙子皮来代替橙子片。<ref>{{cite web |title=Negroni |url=https://celticliquor.co.nz/the-old-fashioned-15/ |website=celtic liquor }}{{Dead link}}</ref>

==历史==
[[File:General_Pascal_Olivier_Count_de_Negroni.jpg|thumb]]
虽然这种饮料的起源不详，但最广泛的报道是它于1919年在[[意大利|意大利]][[佛罗伦萨|佛罗伦萨]]位于托纳布奥尼大街的Caffè Casoni（原Caffè Giacosa）首次制作，现在叫Caffè Roberto Cavalli。[[卡米洛·尼格罗尼|卡米洛·尼格罗尼]]（Camillo Negroni ）伯爵要求调酒师[[福斯科·斯卡塞利|福斯科·斯卡塞利]]（Fosco Scarselli）加入[[金酒|金酒]]而不是普通的[[苏打水|苏打水]]，以提高他最喜欢的美式鸡尾酒的烈度。调酒师还额外使用了橙子装饰以表明这是一种不同的鸡尾酒，而不是美式鸡尾酒典型的柠檬装饰。<ref>{{cite news |title=SHAKEN AND STIRRED; Dressing Italian |last=Cecchini |first=Toby |date=2002-10-06 |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |page=913 |accessdate=2009-12-10 |url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9C05E5DF173BF935A35753C1A9649C8B63 }}; {{cite news|title=Negroni history lesson ends in a glass|last=Regan|first=Gary|date=2009-03-29|newspaper=[[San_Francisco_Chronicle|San Francisco Chronicle]]|page=e-6|accessdate=2009-12-14|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2009/03/27/FD8R1696QJ.DTL&type=food|archive-date=2009-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091202070646/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2009%2F03%2F27%2FFD8R1696QJ.DTL&type=food|dead-url=no}}; Luca Picchi, ''Sulle tracce del conte. La vera storia del cocktail Negroni'' (On the Trail of the Count, The True Story of the Negroni Cocktail), Edizioni Plan, Florenz, 2002, {{ISBN|88-88719-16-4}}; {{cite book |title= How's Your Drink?: Cocktails, Culture, and the Art of Drinking Well |url= https://archive.org/details/howsyourdrinkcoc0000felt |last= Felten|first= Eric|year=2007 |publisher= [[Agate_Publishing|Agate Surrey]]|isbn=1-57284-089-7 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/howsyourdrinkcoc0000felt/page/207 207] |id=ANSXqicDb4IC&lpg=PT68&dq=negroni%20%20james%20bond&pg=PT69#v=onepage&q=negroni%20%20count&f=false }}</ref>

在新的鸡尾酒大获成功后，尼格罗尼家族就在意大利[[特雷维索|特雷维索]]成立了尼格罗尼酒厂并生产一种预制的饮料，在1919年以“古老的尼格罗尼”的名义出售。<ref name="mixerplanet">{{cite web |publisher=Mixer Planet|url=http://www.mixerplanet.com/campari-academy-storia-negroni_32571/|title= Campari Academy e la Storia del Negroni|date=2014-10-22|accessdate=2018-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160622045919/http://www.mixerplanet.com/campari-academy-storia-negroni_32571/ |archive-date=2016-06-22 }}</ref> 关于这杯鸡尾酒最早的报道之一来自于1947年[[奥森·威尔斯|奥森·威尔斯]]（Orson Welles）在[[罗马|罗马]]拍摄《卡格里奥斯特罗》（Cagliostro）时与《科肖顿论坛报》（Coshocton Tribune）的信件，他在信件中描述了一种名为尼格罗尼的新饮料：“[[苦精|苦精]]对你的肝脏很好，金酒对你的肝脏不好。它们会互相平衡。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://dictionary.oed.com/cgi/entry/00322657?single=1&query_type=word&queryword=negroni&first=1&max_to_show=10|title= Oxford English Dictionary negroni |date=Dec 2009 |accessdate=2009-12-29|quote=The bitters are excellent for your liver, the gin is bad for you. They balance each other.}}; [[Coshocton_Tribune|Coshocton Tribune]], 17 December 1947</ref>

鸡尾酒历史学家[[大卫·万德瑞奇|大卫·万德瑞奇]]（David Wondrich）研究了关于卡米洛·尼格罗尼（Camillo Negroni）的故事，他指出尼格罗尼的伯爵身份值得怀疑，但他的祖父[[路易吉·尼格罗尼|路易吉·尼格罗尼]]（Luigi Negroni）确实是个伯爵。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Regan|first1=Gary|title=The Negroni: Drinking to La Dolce Vita, with Recipes & Lore|date=2015|publisher=Potter/TenSpeed/Harmony|isbn=1607747804|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=IZdoBAAAQBAJ&dq=count+camillo+negroni+wondrich&source=gbs_navlinks_s|accessdate=2017-06-28}}</ref>

帕斯卡尔·奥利维尔伯爵·德·尼格罗尼将军的后人说，他就是1857年在塞内加尔发明这种饮料的尼格罗尼伯爵。1980年的一篇在《科尔斯马汀周日版》的文章说他在1914年左右发明了这种饮料。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://captainnoelxaviernegroni.tumblr.com/|title=The newspaper article, "Corse Matin, 1980", Pascal|access-date=2014-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208185024/http://captainnoelxaviernegroni.tumblr.com/|archive-date=2015-12-08}}</ref>在《新罕布什尔州联盟领袖》的一篇文章报道了这一争议。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.unionleader.com/article/20140619/LOCALVOICES08/140618850|title=Mark Hayward's City Matters|work=UnionLeader.com|accessdate=2020-08-03|archive-date=2018-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180922035537/http://www.unionleader.com/article/20140619/LOCALVOICES08/140618850|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==变种==
<!-- please only include variations that either have articles, or reliable sources -->
* 美式：1盎司[[金巴利|金巴利]]，1盎司甜红[[苦艾酒|苦艾酒]]，一小杯苏打水。
* 勃拉瓦第：用威士忌代替金酒。
* 老朋友：同时使用干苦艾酒和加拿大[[黑麦威士忌|黑麦威士忌]]。
* Agavoni或Tegroni：用[[龙舌兰酒|龙舌兰酒]]替金酒。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Englesh|first1=Camper|title=Negroni Cocktail. Der Playboy Unter Den Klassikern|trans-title=Negroni Cocktail. The Playboy Among The Classics|url=http://mixology.eu/klassik/negroni-der-playboy-unter-den-klassikern/2/|accessdate=2016-12-16|work=Mixology.eu|date=2012-01-01|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180109183039/http://mixology.eu/klassik/negroni-der-playboy-unter-den-klassikern/2/|archive-date=2018-01-09}}</ref>
* 荷兰尼格罗尼酒：使用荷兰干金酒代替伦敦干金酒。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://liquor.com/recipes/dutch-negroni-2/#skyPYe1LeMhgCESa.97|title=Dutch Negroni|accessdate=2020-08-03|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807174810/https://www.liquor.com/recipes/dutch-negroni-2/#skyPYe1LeMhgCESa.97|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* Fergroni：使用潘脱红蜜[[味美思|味美思]]代替苦艾酒。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://stjohnrestaurant.com/products/the-fergroni-aka-negroni-as-it-should-be|title=Fergroni|accessdate=2020-08-03|archive-date=2020-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200124174150/https://stjohnrestaurant.com/products/the-fergroni-aka-negroni-as-it-should-be|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* “错误的”尼格罗尼：用起泡[[白葡萄酒|白葡萄酒]]或[[普罗塞克|普罗塞克]]代替金酒 。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.campari.com/int/en/cocktails/list/negroni-sbagliato/|title=Campari Negroni sbagliato cocktail recipe|work=Campari|access-date=2014-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915134204/http://www.campari.com/int/en/cocktails/list/negroni-sbagliato/|archive-date=2016-09-15}}</ref>
* 白尼格罗尼：使用金酒、[[利莱白开胃酒|利莱白开胃酒]]和[[苏兹|苏兹]]调制。<ref>{{cite news |last=Allan |first=M. Carrie |date=2017-07-07 |title=The White Negroni Has Become a New Classic |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/food/some-negroni-spinoffs-have-spun-too-far-but-one-has-become-a-new-classic/2017/07/06/18d161c0-6258-11e7-8adc-fea80e32bf47_story.html |work=The Washington Post |location=Washington, D.C. |accessdate=2020-08-03 |archive-date=2018-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181202011800/https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/food/some-negroni-spinoffs-have-spun-too-far-but-one-has-become-a-new-classic/2017/07/06/18d161c0-6258-11e7-8adc-fea80e32bf47_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

